# Kim tra s gi tr Null  cc thuc tnh:
feature_cols = df.columns
def display_null(df, feature_cols):
    n_rows = df.shape[0]
    for col in feature_cols:
        null_count = df[col].isnull().sum()
        if null_count > 0:
            print(f"{col} has {null_count*100/n_rows:.2f}% null values.")

display_null(df, feature_cols)

In [66]:
Q1 = np.percentile(df1['Price'],25)
Q3 = np.percentile(df1['Price'], 75)

IQR = Q3 - Q1

threshold_lower = Q1 - 1.5*IQR
threshold_upper = Q3 + 1.5*IQR

df1 = df1[(df1['Price'] >= threshold_lower) & (df1['Price'] <= threshold_upper)]

import folium
from folium.plugins import HeatMap

coordinates_list = []
for coord_str in location['Coordinates']:
    coord = coord_str.strip('()').split(',')
    coordinates_list.append((float(coord[0]), float(coord[1])))

m = folium.Map(location=[16.07729181528557, 108.22274899303063], zoom_start=14)

heat_map = HeatMap(coordinates_list)

m.add_child(heat_map)

m
